      "writtenOn": "2016-02-17T06:21:06Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yes. If some tokens manage to outlive the EvenSubscriber that generated them, they\u0027ll be invalidated by EventSubscriber\u0027s dtor and the lambda will never be invoked by them after EventSubscriber\u0027s demise.",
      "parentUuid": "dd7ab832_d4ca7293",
      "range": {
