      "writtenOn": "2016-02-16T23:09:40Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "the lifetimes are really scary here - you\u0027ve a unique_ptr with a raw pointer stored, some lambdas which capture this, destructors conditionally calling into functions. Is it possible to describe the object lifetimes in some comment?",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 69,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 72,
        "endChar": 17
      },
      "revId": "b2c03cf43d66463647ff05faa79d8d71b726ed3b",
